# Luxanvoryx Data Models

This document outlines the core data models used in the app.

## Drink Model
```dart
class Drink {
  final String name;
  final int volume; // in ml
  final int caffeine; // in mg
  final DateTime time;
  final String icon; // icon identifier
  final String category; // e.g., coffee, tea, energy drink
}
```

## Coupon Model
```dart
class Coupon {
  final String title;
  final String description;
  final DateTime expiryDate;
  final String category; // e.g., dining, shopping, travel
  final String iconName;
  final bool isUsed;
}
```

## ColorScheme Model
```dart
class ColorScheme {
  final int hue; // 0-360
  final double saturation; // 0-100
  final double lightness; // 0-100
  final String name; // optional name for saved schemes
  final DateTime createdAt;
}
```

## Data Storage
- Use shared_preferences for simple data storage
- Store models as JSON strings
- Implement helper methods for serialization/deserialization
